<p>
    <strong>How will you contribute? </strong>
</p>
<p>
    Just be you. Represent for your school, your interests, and bring your curiosity. A lot is changing with schools as they are implementing digital
    curriculum. There is more sophistication needed beyond what device to select. The world of digital content and curriculum is enormously complex now.
    Therefore, it’s important to bring the curriculum and IT worlds together with district leadership to learn about, and discuss, a complete strategy.
</p>
<p>
    I and my staff host these events, which are educational and sponsored by several vendors from the high tech and digital curriculum community. We work with
    our sponsors to prepare them to contribute to the conversation in meaningful ways.
</p>
<p>
    You’ll be surprised at how much you gain from an old-fashioned day of peer discussion.
</p>
<p>
